channel.title: AntiLag Problem
channel.description:
Hey guys. Just re-installed Mopar and my old server (Parents). And I've tried to access my server, compiled and got this;
antilag.java:4: error while writing antilag: antilag.class (Access is denied) public class antilag ^
Does anyone know what this means? Thanks.

item.title: AntiLag Problem
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

It means the old antilag class file is read only. Delete it and then recompile.
